# Local Environment

## Installed locally

- Python
- Docker

## NOT installed locally

- Node.js
- Go, Java, Rust, C#, GCC…

## Running demos and tests

- If the language runtime is installed locally, run commands directly
- Otherwise, use Docker:

```powershell
docker run --rm -v "${PWD}:/app" -w /app <image> <command>
```

Example for Node.js tests:

```powershell
docker run --rm -v "${PWD}:/app" -w /app node:22-slim node --test index.test.js
```
